This is a Fightyard Map in the Location of a Fantasy Snow Map. Thats a small battle Map.
Maybe you like to edit the Map to a Gun Game Map (The Hammer Files into the Pack)
On Map Spawn all Player are have a Deagle. I have put 2 HE Grenades on the Overpass.
There is a Ambient Wind Sound into the Map. I have addet a NAV File into the Pack, so you can play with BOTS.
Have Fun
